data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-story brick home on a oversized corner lot! Featuring 3 bedrooms + dedicated office, this spacious home is flooded with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a cozy living room featuring a beautiful fireplace, perfect for those chilly evenings. The wood flooring adds a touch of elegance and warmth to the space. The open kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting granite countertops and ample storage space. The primary bedroom is an airy retreat with large windows that allow plenty of natural light to pour in. The primary bathroom is like a private spa with a luxurious tub and shower combination, providing a perfect place to unwind after a long day. Upstairs, you'll discover a bonus flex space that can be customized to suit your needs. Outside, you'll find a large fenced backyard, perfect for hosting outdoor gatherings. Other standout features include a sprinkler system and whole-home water filter.
